dataqual.logic:
This dataset is based upon a combined set of city and community boundaries. The city boundaries are derived from the Assessor City Boundaries. Community boundaries are extracted from the following two sources:
1) Thomas Brothers 2005 ZipCode Boundaries, with primary USPS Postal Community Names assigned to the boundary. Primarily assigned to unincorporated areas and LA City (San Fernando Valley portion). Stored in the PO_Name field
2) LA County Regional Planning Statistical Area Boundaries - used as a secondary source of LA County Unincorporated Areas and LA City (non San Fernando Valley). Stored in the Statname field.
Since the original creation, a number of changes have been made:
April 2006 - Addition of Downtown Los Angeles July 2005 - inclusion of Palmdale and Santa Clarita Annexations
